metadata.name: REINK CITY (II)
metadata.description:
The exact location. Coordinates on the map.
Reink City. Open the portal to come as you please, be and live as you wish.
The elf Quasar left the other world behind. 
Mama Shu is upstairs accessing the oracles and coordinating the fragments. 
Everyone feels the light and shadow and decides where to go. We are no longer alone.
The first ritual is remarkable. Dissolve what the eyes see and realign again.
Pixels everywhere, portals opened, some go, others arrive. 
Experiences and moments of the past and present in a future where we can feel our deepest and most naive yearnings.
Time and space. The mind resides in other skins. 
Make these bodies your home again.

7500x2250

The first owner will receive a framed poster sized artwork and a NFT avatar inspired by this scene to be released on Opensea in 2022. Additionally, access to whitelist of planned exclusive fashion items inspired by my NFT works.
